data.description: This home offers TWO SEPARATE LIVING QUARTERS with both levels having their own entrances! The main level includes a living room (with a fireplace & built-ins!), dining room, three bedrooms, full bathroom, & a stackable laundry closet. Access your back patio from the living room, or from the kitchen which offers a gas range, and updated countertops & backsplash. Head to the 2nd living quarters on the basement level for an eat-in kitchen, large living room, two bedrooms, full bath, & separate utility/laundry room. Out back, the home features a raised patio & spacious fenced backyard with storage shed. With some TLC, this just may be the investment opportunity you've been searching for! Refrigerator on main level & both Washer/Dryer sets will convey. Conveniently located with quick access to US-321, near shopping, restaurants, George Pappas Liberty Lanes, the growing FUSE District of Downtown Gastonia, & minutes from I-85.
